																},
																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "ha62d2848g4c13g48aeg98fcg1461baf0dbab",
																	"value": "I hope Shadowheart's parents are a welcome balm for her wounds. There will be pain in defying such a malicious goddess, but perhaps no more than in obeying her.",
