																},
																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "hdcf16664g6726g43f8gbca9gebc8be3bf333",
																	"value": "A real githyanki crèche. Few outsiders learn the secrets of such places. Fewer still live to share their observations. A keen eye and a quiet tongue may serve us well here.",
